{"tid":1802400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】今集頭條堅高質!","createTime":"2019-12-29T12:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T14:13:53.000Z","uid":321887,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"49b9ab3396d01d7742f23feadf17bb6a80436145","tid":1802400,"uid":321887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:18:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lZSq6s1XTsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlZSq6s1XTsA&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK94ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=aa60daee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lZSq6s1XTsA</a><br />\n<br />\n完全分析到林鄭每一步棋點走，大家可以借鑒繼續擴大民意基礎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d33fac74664a1268b9716bf0e48ae7e774629c","tid":1802400,"uid":321887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:19:31.000Z","msg":"五推收手 (1/5)"},{"pid":"700711a4aa3affb53003494a1bc6a7817e41398e","tid":1802400,"uid":321887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:19:42.000Z","msg":"五推收手 (2/5)"},{"pid":"c9be57118ef3542253338a05204a597e216a85f4","tid":1802400,"uid":321887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:19:53.000Z","msg":"五推收手 (3/5)"},{"pid":"3481983db7d99bd0332660457a83f3566cd690af","tid":1802400,"uid":321887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:20:03.000Z","msg":"五推收手 (4/5)"},{"pid":"381f2d86900901a441144c85679e82f0f0db0c1f","tid":1802400,"uid":321887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"五推收手 (5/5)"},{"pid":"c91ff7595aff73104d286fe1ba8d81527a9c6c05","tid":1802400,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:21:03.000Z","msg":"突發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZuNAtv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZuNAtv.png&h=a8f19de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不反都出埋唔好再搵藉口唔出<br />\n1月1號維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n【元旦大遊行　不反已出】<br />\n<br />\n民陣已收到警方發出的不反對通知書，<br />\n可以正式同各位講多次，1.1 維園見！<br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行當日將會有超過 40 個新成立工會同大家見面，歡迎大家了解詳情，加入你所屬行業的工會，壯大抗爭的組織力量。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n一月一，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認住831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f46cddeca88bd6279773d250a11d69c84d36655","tid":1802400,"uid":321887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1月1維園見</span>"},{"pid":"8b702cf2b9173460e2831fb2e82dabe380ecd83e","tid":1802400,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EpeFbjp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpeFbjp.jpg&h=1453d793&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd520e951c77a7067d8aeb1ce18d5b77fce646ea","tid":1802400,"uid":321887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林奠要同成個香港敵對!</span>"},{"pid":"13cfe3c3d778734bbc5ff7e0b417b964d1eb9127","tid":1802400,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:34:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ee436a1fcc98eb79e41052ab9200e7ecf2fb3fb","tid":1802400,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor